154
00:09:18.892 --> 00:09:20.185
That's the last time I saw him.

155
00:09:20.268 --> 00:09:21.561
Why'd you have his coat?

156
00:09:21.644 --> 00:09:22.896
The door. Always opening.

157
00:09:22.979 --> 00:09:25.315
