I don't even know
who this kid is. but...

190
00:12:18.613 --> 00:12:20.490
Tell your sister you'll
call her back. We gotta talk.

191
00:12:20.573 --> 00:12:22.409
Did you not hear me when I said
I had a death in the family?

192
00:12:22.492 --> 00:12:23.827
I did.

193
00:12:23.910 --> 00:12:25.370
I need to get my affairs
in order.

194
