and then I... I'm all yours?

200
00:12:48.977 --> 00:12:50.437
Swing by the station.

201
00:12:50.520 --> 00:12:51.813
I'll be there.

202
00:12:52.897 --> 00:12:53.898
Great.

203
00:12:55.150 --> 00:12:56.902
Condolences again.

204
00:12:56.985 --> 00:12:58.194
Appreciate you.

205
00:13:48.703 --> 00:13:49.830
When I showed him
the photograph.

206
00:13:49.913 --> 00:13:51.957
he said he never saw the kid.

207
00:13:52.040 --> 00:13:53.250
But he got pissed at you.

208
00:13:53.333 --> 00:13:56.086
Annoyed. And I was pushing him.

209
00:13:56.169 --> 00:13:58.380
Dead uncle? I might be the same.

210
00:13:58.463 --> 00:14:00.132
What do you think?

211
00:14:00.215 --> 00:14:02.259
I think two people said
they saw them together.

212
00:14:02.342 --> 00:14:04.011
No.

213
00:14:04.094 --> 00:14:06.221
Two people said that Rob Piest
said they were together.

214
00:14:06.304 --> 00:14:08.265
Nobody saw 'em.

215
00:14:08.348 --> 00:14:09.391
What do you think?

216
00:14:11.142 --> 00:14:12.436
That I spent
enough time undercover.

217
00:14:12.519 --> 00:14:14.896
being lied to. in the eye.

218
00:14:16.147 --> 00:14:18.191
No. the kid was with him.

219
00:14:18.274 --> 00:14:20.152
And I think we need to get
a warrant for that house.

220
00:14:20.235 --> 00:14:21.569
Yeah. Yeah. it's me.

221
00:14:23.530 --> 00:14:26.032
Yeah. I need everything
that Chicago PD's got on a guy.

222
00:14:27.409 --> 00:14:29.328
And I need a favor ASAP.

223
00:14:29.411 --> 00:14:31.163
G-A-C-Y.

224
00:14:31.246 --> 00:14:32.289
Thank you. sir.

225
00:14:32.372 --> 00:14:33.415
First name. John Wayne.

226
00:14:33.498 --> 00:14:35.125
Hello. How we doing?

227
00:14:35.208 --> 00:14:37.002
-Yeah. Yeah.
-Hiya. How's it going?

228
00:14:37.085 --> 00:14:38.295
Like Rooster Cogburn.

229
00:14:38.378 --> 00:14:39.963
Good to see you. gentlemen.

230
00:14:43.591 --> 00:14:44.968
Thank you. officer.

231
00:14:45.051 --> 00:14:46.470
-Mr. Gacy.
-Hi.

232
00:14:46.553 --> 00:14:47.930
