Joe Kozenczak.

234
00:14:50.015 --> 00:14:51.058
Mr. Gacy.

235
00:14:51.141 --> 00:14:52.392
Yeah. Anything to help.

236
00:14:52.475 --> 00:14:54.186
And. and John's fine.
Drop the mister.

237
00:14:54.269 --> 00:14:57.356
I don't know who the hell
you're talking about. right?

238
00:14:57.439 --> 00:14:59.191
Couldn't make it in last night?
I waited for you.

239
00:14:59.274 --> 00:15:00.359
Oh. jeez.

240
00:15:00.442 --> 00:15:02.486
Family and then a car accident.

241
00:15:02.569 --> 00:15:05.072
Can you believe it?
When it rains.

242
00:15:05.155 --> 00:15:06.365
Everything all right?

243
00:15:06.448 --> 00:15:08.408
Oh. yeah. Everything's fine.

244
00:15:09.534 --> 00:15:11.370
I just got a contusion
of the ego.

245
00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:15.540
Black ice.
I slipped off the road.

246
00:15:15.623 --> 00:15:17.960
Guy with a truck pulled me out.

247
00:15:18.043 --> 00:15:21.213
Well. don't suppose anything's
changed since yesterday.

248
00:15:21.296 --> 00:15:23.382
but what we're all trying
to figure out

249
00:15:23.465 --> 00:15:25.384
