to think you met with this kid.

250
00:15:25.467 --> 00:15:26.510
Right. Yeah.

251
00:15:26.593 --> 00:15:28.720
Me too. Uh.

252
00:15:28.803 --> 00:15:32.391
well. maybe he was saying

253
00:15:32.474 --> 00:15:34.476
that he wanted to meet with me

254
00:15:34.559 --> 00:15:38.563
