right?

255
00:15:38.646 --> 00:15:40.065
Successful.

256
00:15:40.148 --> 00:15:42.317
Lots of jobs and employees.

257
00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:44.486
Mostly high school kids. yeah?

258
00:15:46.154 --> 00:15:47.614
Cops do cop things.

259
00:15:49.491 --> 00:15:50.575
Yeah.

260
00:15:50.658 --> 00:15:52.160
I'm giving 'em a chance
to learn a skill.

261
00:15:52.243 --> 00:15:53.287
Keep 'em out of trouble.

262
00:15:53.370 --> 00:15:55.122
They look at me.
see what they could be.

263
00:15:55.205 --> 00:15:57.165
Anamosa State Penitentiary?

264
00:15:59.584 --> 00:16:00.752
Cops do cop things.

265
